{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "a3ba2fab-6bac-463e-9b62-389d5f69a25b", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a3ba2fab-6bac-463e-9b62-389d5f69a25b@1.pkg/1772597670076/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597670917", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/a3ba2fab-6bac-463e-9b62-389d5f69a25b@1.pkg/1772597670076/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597670917"}, "identifier": "a3ba2fab-6bac-463e-9b62-389d5f69a25b", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">本题考查对养成健康生活方式。</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">A：司法保护通常指司法机关采取的措施，而题干中的文件由国务院印发，属于政府保护，故A说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">B：&ldquo;确保学生的全面发展&rdquo;表述绝对化，故B说法错误；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">C：加强体育课和运动会直接促进学生锻炼身体，有助于养成健康生活方式，故C符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"background: #FFFFFF;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">D：题干措施侧重增强体质，与&ldquo;养护精神&rdquo;和&ldquo;科学文化素养&rdquo;无直接关联，故D不符合题意；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">故本题选C。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）2025年1月，国务院印发的《教育强国建设规划纲要（2024&md